divs: sighting details from 2001 to 2004 i lived on the sc ind.res. nm which is 10 miles ne of los alamos nat.lab. i'm an artist and love to take pics of wonderful cloud formations, so at sunset i sat outside w my camera, looking west. 1st i saw a jet(w the usual exhaust-trail) heading from n.to w., passing thru 2 separate clouds, at about 25,000 feet. after it disappeared from view here comes another shiny object(from same direction) and it enters cloud #1, but it never came out\passed thru the 1st cloud!! (it somehow stayed in\behind the cloud.) and it dawned on me: there was no ex.trail accompanying it! i sat transfixed and in about 2 min. it suddenly re-appeared and sped-away much faster than it had arrived, in the same direction it had come from... sure wish i'd had a video camera instead of an slr.
trends: There has been one other sighting in Santa Clara Pueblo

Summary: Streaking object with NO Jet Trail!!
